BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-05-28-1800-studiotwothree@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260504T130230Z
DTSTART:20260528T180000
DTEND:20260528T210000
SUMMARY:Figure Drawing - 5/28
LOCATION:Studio Two Three\, 109 W 15th St\, Richmond\, VA 23224
DESCRIPTION:3-hour figure drawing workshop with professional nude model. Instructor Carter Helmandollar calls poses — short gestural poses\, short poses\, and longer poses. Artists bring their own materials\; extra paper/pencils/clipboards available. No photography permitted.\\n\\nCost: $20.00\\n\\nRegister: https://www.studiotwothree.org/classes/p/figure-drawing-528
URL:https://www.studiotwothree.org/classes/p/figure-drawing-528
END:VEVENT
